{
  "stem": "26142.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every day I had three hours' tutoring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the good fortune was that we had, in Torun, a library.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At the Hebrew-- the Hebrew school had a library.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and the library-- it wasn't common in-- in-- in the small villages to-- to have libraries.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In our libraries, we had books that were from classical writers translated into Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that time, and in the city of [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Vilna ?] in Lithuania, the Jewish organization by the name of [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Yeda Yevoh-- ?] that exists now in New York City, part of it-- which is the acronym [YIDDISH] Institute.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They-- they've actually reorganized the Yiddish language, because the language was chaotic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In each area, everybody wrote, it had no grammar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they organized the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they also translated the most famous works of literary classical writers like Tolstoy, Gorky and Pushkin, Byron-- I remember [? mappa sohn, ?] and for instance, reading in Yiddish, or from Tolstoy, and others.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was not-- you couldn't find that in every village in the Carpathian.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was unique.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told you that I just got that book that was published in Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it writes about the neighboring village-- which was only four kilometers-- Bystre.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it says there that even though they were only for kilometers from Torun, they had very little influence by the Zionist movement that was in Torun.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were a few that left even from there-- but very few.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Torun-- the Torun youth emigrated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's after the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Out of the 800 people that lived there, after the war we had over 100 survivors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a large percentage of survivors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the reason for it was because of the Zionist movement was strong in Torun .",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
